2. The model checkpoint is madeby561/GLM-5.2-MXFP8-NVFP4-NF3-Hybrid
   (https://huggingface.co/madeby561/GLM-5.2-MXFP8-NVFP4-NF3-Hybrid),
   licensed under MIT. Not distributed in this repository.

