4. The b12x CUDA-graph-safe decode kernel is from
   voipmonitor/b12x (https://github.com/voipmonitor/b12x).

5. The container image build harness is adapted from
   m9e/blackwell-llm-docker
   (https://github.com/m9e/blackwell-llm-docker), which itself derives
   from eugr/spark-vllm-docker
   (https://github.com/eugr/spark-vllm-docker).

6. The serve configuration incorporates tuning contributed on the NVIDIA
   developer forums by Zatz (unpruned QuantTrio recipe, thread 374125
